pageTitle: Itinerary for Tuesday, August 23, 2016 | Prime Minister of Canada
articleHtml:
Itinerary for the Prime Minister, Justin Trudeau, for Tuesday, August 23, 2016:

Barrie, Ontario

9:30 a.m. The Prime Minister will make an announcement with the Premier of Ontario, Kathleen Wynne, and the Mayor of the City of Barrie, Jeff Lehman. A joint media availability will follow.

Barrie Transit Garage
133 Welham Road
Barrie, Ontario

Notes for media:

  • Open media coverage
  • Media should arrive no later than 8:45 a.m.

PMO Media Relations:
media@pmo-cpm.gc.ca
613-957-5555
